summary: so my 7 year old brother is kind of behind on Andi Mack so I was filling in important info for him for example, Bex and Bowie...
body: so my 7 year old brother is kind of behind on Andi Mack so I was filling in important info for him for example, Bex and Bowie are getting married, Walker is Buffy’s new boo, not Andi’s, and about Tyrus. Then as a joke I told him that TJ and Cyrus are actually getting married too. He was so shocked but then told me he doesn’t believe me and tbh I was expecting him to say something like “Boys can’t get married!” but instead he was like “I know you’re lying because they’re only in middle school, they can’t get married yet.” When I tell you I never loved my baby brother more than I did in that moment.
